{"tid":757283,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"明將都有高汁嘅分店？","createTime":"2018-07-26T16:56:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-31T05:27:39.000Z","uid":11293,"like":32,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"8ce67092c58333162cf73373ee07394e55d80004","tid":757283,"uid":11293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T16:56:00.000Z","msg":"想當年，小弟仲係中學生，明將係圍內friend嘅笑話，成日用「挑戰明將紅豆軍艦」作係懲罰。<br />\n<br />\n但其實喺2011年（大約呢個時間）之前，佐敦有間明將非常高質（比起其他明將），當中特製嘅吉列炸蠔卷，我係到而家都記得個味道。<br />\n<br />\n可惜佢2011年執咗。<br />\n<br />\n有無人都有食過呢間分店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6efd098d5e45d9ae1a7749265e2618462beb0aee","tid":757283,"uid":117552,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T17:33:33.000Z","msg":"佐敦明將真心正"},{"pid":"b5496a36c3f7678f1d69d278ea8332ac2b93e47c","tid":757283,"uid":35678,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T17:35:04.000Z","msg":"佐敦明將的確世界級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b827b5662b1d8424bae5f6d582f1d488d1ad1775","tid":757283,"uid":171119,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T19:34:01.000Z","msg":"好似食過，但太耐以前無咩記憶，印象中整體係唔錯仲食左好多"},{"pid":"34ad71b5399d64e3673c23a1a73d8025e1c5cadd","tid":757283,"uid":192664,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T19:48:47.000Z","msg":"佐敦名將真係好掂，晚晚排隊排到落樓梯，最正係燒牛肉壽司，每次得4碟，次次都比坐師傅前面d客攞晒，仲個金毛mk師傅成個言承旭咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nOff topic 一下，嗰時隔離街山林道金鳳夜晚食個鐵板jar jar聲都只係60零蚊，依家d嘢真係貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ba09d56beafc8d1b3201008d9f61a9eebaac21c","tid":757283,"uid":99700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T23:27:28.000Z","msg":"食過 以前專登去食"},{"pid":"2e08dc75dbb25bf434a65668dc01375b678ba089","tid":757283,"uid":35608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy